{"tid":205003,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC][Alpha] Rust 大家一齊玩啦","createTime":"2017-04-17T12:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T05:44:56.000Z","uid":79546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"737ba5c61955692835a0f81dfef44ed0a99757ca","tid":205003,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/17/204126_1d9f5f2f067e0013ac9c63cf76fe47c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F17%2F204126_1d9f5f2f067e0013ac9c63cf76fe47c1.jpg&h=20d475d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRust係一隻多人PVP野外生存遊戲，玩家一開始只得石頭同火把，衫都冇件。玩家可以收集不同資源，起屋同武器。殺動物去攞食物。除左會餓同口渴，玩家都會受唔同地方因素影響，包活温度、濕度等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他玩家可以互相打鬥，入侵人地屋企，所以起一間靚嘅屋係重要一環。<br />\n<br />\n  地圖上有多處建築，入面有好多貴重物品，但大部分建築物區域都有幅射。<br />\n<br />\n介紹住咁多先，遲啲再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">Steam購買網頁:</span><a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/252490/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F252490%2F&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraYzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=718a4544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/252490/</a></span>"},{"pid":"d2ba57c95cbcacb2f3aea32978b0910be5271543","tid":205003,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:41:09.000Z","msg":"勁耐以前玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個server洗左之後就唔想玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd49a4db63fab646ca659bed1ac86c863abafb0","tid":205003,"uid":69792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"啱啱出個陣就有玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開個group一齊玩？"},{"pid":"d0d4ee650a8db57fc550e2f66e11586f87791721","tid":205003,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:01:01.000Z","msg":"依隻GAME更新完 用GTX760已經推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486e525d6164e85ddf7906210b0c4b27a368cd27","tid":205003,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"比堆支那人打死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要防守了"},{"pid":"e5db0f449e7bd29c1d3222d7c34557bc26346601","tid":205003,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱出個陣就有玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開個group一齊玩？</blockquote><br />\nDiscord好嗎？"},{"pid":"f736ae2a126d0fff5ae755b75a5fc6dab5bc283d","tid":205003,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依隻GAME更新完 用GTX760已經推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最低都唔得？"},{"pid":"b802df507eccab0340915ff310a53c971df6bc66","tid":205003,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:29:23.000Z","msg":"依家活躍於Hong Kong 1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2daf9cfb3cb065605f53fba0872132c3e92ff456","tid":205003,"uid":58732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T00:49:57.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"af2a1c677f858d51ac2c8c1e814885d838587702","tid":205003,"uid":79546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:17:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新手教學</span></span><br />\n每個人一開始都會有兩樣野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h5GH83U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh5GH83U.jpg&h=a9421e57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/181230_e7f30e0addb5dc5a2b6375e8f86b555d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F181230_e7f30e0addb5dc5a2b6375e8f86b555d.jpg&h=fbeffdc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n石頭同火把<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">石頭</span><br />\n用嚟收集資訊，樹同石都得。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">火把</span><br />\n只係用嚟照明，冇乜攻擊力，冇得用作資源收集。<br />\n<br />\n新仔如果有朋友嘅，第一件事一定係揾木頭，整一張紙，再用紙整地圖，睇下自己係邊先。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/181538_71c96e4985b39f666479a7b67b60a481.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F181538_71c96e4985b39f666479a7b67b60a481.jpg&h=4b4a7882&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">-&gt;</span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35X9chz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35X9chz.jpg&h=11f4c377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地圖控制係Mouse右鍵，包括移動、畫圖、放大縮小。"},{"pid":"8988f49f9d01e55c740fea5cc319f10d6ede936d","tid":205003,"uid":79546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:29:59.000Z","msg":"收集左木頭同石，之後就可以整工具，令自己可以收集更多資源。<br />\n<br />\n基本上有以下三個主要工具。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34e8N07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34e8N07.jpg&h=46db4eea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r389xeX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr389xeX.jpg&h=d0a79e46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/181827_7cfff3d8e0f12ecbbe4cd5b539496d11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F181827_7cfff3d8e0f12ecbbe4cd5b539496d11.jpg&h=f7fbb249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斧頭用嚟收木，鎬就用嚟收石，骨刀就用嚟收屍體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起屋就用計劃圖，起地基、牆、門等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79nCLb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79nCLb6.jpg&h=20316965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n起好門後記得用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>門鎖</strong></span></span>，簡單嘅就用鎖匙，開住門、對住個鎖就可以整多條鎖匙。有多啲資源嘅，就用密碼鎖，如果有人想撞密碼，就會電佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當你收集到一定嘅資源之後，你就可以起爐頭，放啲木同鐵礦入去，燒完之後就有鐵。"},{"pid":"9731366fed1720908a73c66cc2809298918b3c71","tid":205003,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83996a6a7b9078588bc31ae06253e93d0371cc77","tid":205003,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7eb7119177bbcb6069784c02026bf212c3a5837c","tid":205003,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85e90399a168df4c4db94f40b89636652156f19","tid":205003,"uid":58732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:35:41.000Z","msg":"Hongkong1 係咪執左"},{"pid":"ad3eb97e98f3c67edf50d4b52feac48fa0965586","tid":205003,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T05:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hongkong1 係咪執左</blockquote><br />\n暫時係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\"